### 6. INSTAGRAM AUDIT SECTION (InstagramAuditSection.js)

**Location: `/Users/gabiorma/gormaran-ai-growth-hub/src/components/InstagramAuditSection.js` (lines 182-617)**

**Key difference from regular tools:** InstagramAuditSection **handles its own authentication**:

```javascript
async function handleGenerate(e) {
  e.preventDefault();
  if (!bio.trim() || !goal) {
    setError(t('ig.error.required', { defaultValue: 'Please fill in the required fields: bio and main goal.' }));
    return;
